---
layout: base.njk
current: sessions
permalink: /sessions/
title: Songs That Found Me at the Right Time
description: "Intimate films where artists share the one song that found them at the right time, and carried them through. A co-production of Sounds of Saving and the 988 Suicide and Crisis Lifeline."
ogType: website
---
<style>
  .sessions-page { padding-block: var(--space-xl); }

  /* — Editorial header — */
  .sessions-head { max-width: var(--maxw-prose); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); }
  .sessions-head .eyebrow { display: block; margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xs); }
  .sessions-head h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-title);
    line-height: var(--lh-tight);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
  }
  .sessions-intro {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-lead);
    line-height: var(--lh-base);
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
  }
  .sessions-cobrand {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-tiny);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .sessions-cobrand strong { color: var(--accent); font-weight: var(--fw-regular); }

  .sessions-toolbar {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: baseline;
    margin: var(--space-md) 0 var(--space-lg);
    padding-top: var(--space-md);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .sessions-toolbar a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-tiny);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .sessions-count {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-tiny);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
  }

  /* — Section labels — */
  .sessions-section + .sessions-section { margin-top: var(--space-xl); }
  .sessions-section__label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-tiny);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  /* — Grid — */
  .sessions-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .sessions-grid--lead { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr)); }

  .session-card { display: flex; }
  .session-card__link {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    width: 100%;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
  }
  .session-card__link:hover .session-card__artist,
  .session-card__link:focus-visible .session-card__artist { color: var(--accent); }

  .session-card .media { aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; }
  .session-card .media img { height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

  .session-card__play {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 3;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    color: var(--paper);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .session-card__play svg {
    width: 46px;
    height: 46px;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 1px 6px rgba(33, 29, 46, 0.55));
    opacity: 0.95;
    transition: transform var(--transition);
  }
  .session-card__link:hover .session-card__play svg { transform: scale(1.08); }

  .session-card__body { padding: var(--space-sm) 0 0; }
  .session-card__artist {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: var(--fw-semibold);
    font-size: var(--fs-h3);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    margin: 0;
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }
  .session-card__song {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-tiny);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin: var(--space-2xs) 0 0;
  }
  .session-card__song .lead { color: var(--accent); }

  /* — Card-wall teaser — */
  .sessions-teaser {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--paper-3);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .sessions-teaser h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-h2);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .sessions-teaser p { font-family: var(--font-body); color: var(--text); margin: 0; max-width: var(--maxw-prose); }
  .sessions-teaser a.btn-text {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-tiny);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    justify-self: start;
  }
</style>

{% macro card(s, lead=false) %}
  <li class="session-card{% if s.featured %} session-card--featured{% endif %}">
    <a class="session-card__link" href="{{ s.url }}">
      <figure class="media media--full">
        {% if s.thumbnail %}<img src="{{ s.thumbnail | img }}" alt="{{ s.artist }} on Songs That Found Me at the Right Time"{% if s.dims %} width="{{ s.dims.width }}" height="{{ s.dims.height }}"{% endif %} loading="lazy" decoding="async" />{% endif %}
        <span class="session-card__play" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
        </span>
      </figure>
      <span class="session-card__body">
        <p class="session-card__artist">{{ s.artist }}</p>
        {% if s.chose %}<p class="session-card__song"><span class="lead">The song:</span> {{ s.chose }}</p>{% endif %}
      </span>
    </a>
  </li>
{% endmacro %}

<div class="container sessions-page">
  <header class="sessions-head">
    <span class="eyebrow">The series</span>
    <h1>Songs That Found Me at the Right Time</h1>
    <p class="sessions-intro">
      Intimate films where artists share the one song that found them at the right time, the song
      that got them through a hard stretch, and tell the story of why it mattered. Music can be a
      lifeline. This is what that sounds like, in their own voices.
    </p>
    <p class="sessions-cobrand">A co-production of <strong>988 Suicide and Crisis Lifeline</strong> &times; <strong>Sounds of Saving</strong></p>
  </header>

  <div class="sessions-toolbar">
    <a href="/sessions/artists/">Browse by artist &rarr;</a>
    <span class="sessions-count">{{ sessions.length }} episodes &middot; 2018 to 2023</span>
  </div>

  {% set featured = sessions | selectattr("featured") | list %}
  {% set rest = sessions | rejectattr("featured") | list %}
  {% set episodes = [] %}
  {% set favorites = [] %}
  {% for s in rest %}
    {% if s.kind == "favorite" %}{% set favorites = (favorites.push(s), favorites) %}
    {% else %}{% set episodes = (episodes.push(s), episodes) %}{% endif %}
  {% endfor %}

  {% if featured.length %}
  <section class="sessions-section" aria-label="Featured episodes">
    <p class="sessions-section__label">Featured</p>
    <ul class="sessions-grid sessions-grid--lead">
      {% for s in featured %}{{ card(s, true) }}{% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  {% if episodes.length %}
  <section class="sessions-section" aria-label="All episodes">
    {% if featured.length %}<p class="sessions-section__label">The series</p>{% endif %}
    <ul class="sessions-grid">
      {% for s in episodes %}{{ card(s) }}{% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  {% if favorites.length %}
  <section class="sessions-section" aria-label="Songs the artists love">
    <p class="sessions-section__label">Songs that found us</p>
    <ul class="sessions-grid">
      {% for s in favorites %}{{ card(s) }}{% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  <aside class="sessions-teaser">
    <h2>Songs That Found Me: the card wall</h2>
    <p>
      Fans are part of this too. Make a card for the song that found you at the right time, share it,
      and add your voice to the wall. It is a small act of solidarity that says: this song carried me,
      and you are not alone.
    </p>
    <a class="btn-text" href="{{ settings.donate_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Make your song card &rarr;</a>
  </aside>
</div>
